{"title_page": "Paul Latzke", "text_new": "{{short description|American football center}}\n{{Infobox NFL biography\n| name                = Paul Latzke\n| image               = \n| image_size          = \n| alt                 = \n| caption             = \n| number              = 52, 54\n| position            = [[Center (gridiron football)|Center]] \n| birth_date          = {{Birth date and age|1942|3|22}}\n| birth_place         = [[Los Angeles]], [[California]]\n| height_ft           = 6\n| height_in           = 4\n| weight_lbs          = 240\n| high_school         = [[Gilroy High School|Gilroy (CA)]]\n| college             = [[Pacific Tigers football|Pacific]]\n| draftyear           = \n| draftround          = \n| draftpick           = \n| pastteams           =\n* [[History of the San Diego Chargers|San Diego Chargers]] ({{NFL Year|1966}}\u2013{{NFL Year|1968}})\n| highlights          =\n}}\n\n'''Paul Latzke''' (born March 22, 1942) is a former [[American football]] [[Center (gridiron football)|center]]. He played for the [[History of the San Diego Chargers|San Diego Chargers]] from 1966 to 1968.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pro-football-reference.com/players/L/LatzPa20.htm |title=Paul Latzke Stats |publisher=Pro-Football-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=2019-05-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/player/paullatzke/2519143/profile |title=Paul Latzke, C |publisher=Nfl.com |date= |accessdate=2019-05-05}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Latzke, Paul}}\n[[Category:1942 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American football centers]]\n[[Category:Pacific Tigers football players]]\n[[Category:San Diego Chargers players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox NFL biography\n| name                = Paul Latzke\n| image               = \n| image_size          = \n| alt                 = \n| caption             = \n| number              = 52, 54\n| position            = [[Center (gridiron football)|Center]] \n| birth_date          = {{Bi