ce Campbell (rugby union)|Campbell]] (5)\n|-\n| 2019-09-07\n| align=left | {{ru|CAN}}\n| 21\n| W, 20-15\n| align=left | {{flagdeco|CAN}} [[BC Place]]\n| \n| [[2019 Rugby World Cup warm-up matches|RWC warm-up]]<ref name=Warmup>{{cite web |url=https://www.usarugby.org/2019/05/u-s-mens-national-team-15s-to-face-rival-canada-in-vancouver-as-final-test-match-before-rugby-world-cup-japan-2019/ |title=U.S. Men\u2019s National Team 15s to face rival-Canada in Vancouver as final test match before Rugby World Cup Japan 2019 |last=Tabani |first=Aalina |date=May 16, 2019 |publisher=[[USA Rugby]] |access-date=May 28, 2019}}</ref>\n| [[Cam Dolan|Dolan]] / [[Dylan Fawsitt|Fawsitt]] / [[Martin Iosefo|Iosefo]] / [[Will Magie|Magie]] (5)\n|-\n| 2019-08-10\n| align=left | {{ru|JPN}}\n| 11\n| L, 20\u201334\n| align=left | {{flagdeco|FJI}} [[ANZ National Stadium]]\n| \n| [[2019 World Rugby Pacific Nations Cup|PNC]]<ref name=PNCSchedule>{{cite web |url=https://www.usarugby.org/2019/04/world-rugby-pacific-nations-cup-kick-off-times-confirmed/ |title=World Rugby Pacific Nations Cup Kick-off Times Confirmed |author=[[World Rugby]] |date=April 25, 2019 |publisher=[[USA Rugby]] |access-date=May 28, 2019}}</ref>\n| [[Will Hooley|Hooley]] (10)\n|-\n| 2019-08-03\n| align=left | {{ru|SAM}}\n| 16\n| W, 13\u201310\n| align=left | {{flagdeco|FJI}} [[ANZ National Stadium]]\n| \n| [[2019 World Rugby Pacific Nations Cup|PNC]]<ref name=PNCSchedule />\n| [[AJ MacGinty|MacGinty]] (13)\n|-\n| 2019-07-27\n| align=left | {{ru|CAN}}\n| 21\n| W, 47\u201319\n| align=left | {{flagdeco|USA}} [[Infinity Park]]\n| 5,000\n| [[2019 World Rugby Pacific Nations Cup|PNC]]<ref name=PNCSchedule />\n| [[AJ MacGinty|MacGinty]] (12)\n|-\n| 2019-03-08\n| align=left | {{ru|CAN}}\n| 21\n| W, 30\u201325\n| align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} [[Starfire Sports]]\n| \n| [[2019 Americas Rugby Championship|ARC]]\n| [[Joe Taufete'e|Taufete'e]] (10)\n|-style=\"background:#fbb;\"\n| 2019-03-02\n| align=left | {{ru|URU}}\n| 17\n| L, 25\u20133